                Featured <span class="text-tanzanian-blue">Moments</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                Highlights from our most memorable community events and celebrations
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Featured Image/Video -->
